name: Misa Amane (弥 海砂) Death note Character LoRA
description:
Trained on AnyLora

V2 Update note -> the goal of this update was to get more character likeness and improve details by improving the dataset and increasing training resolution

Please note that with some enhancers(See description below) it is very easy to get better results than showcased, since i didn't use any to generate showcase images for V2 of this LoRA

To get the best results, please read the description below:

  • Recommended weight for V1/V2: 0.8-1

  • Activation word for V1: Misa

  • Activation word for V2: MisaAmaneV2

  • Upscale to 1.5

  • Use of various enhancers like Detail Tweaker, Beautiful Detailed Eyes, and EnvyBetterHands LoCon is also recommended for best results (See suggested resources)

I would appreciate any reviews, positive or negative!

I would very much appreciate you sharing your results ^_^

If you have any suggestions on what LoRA i should do next, please share them in the comments.

Enjoy :)
